hMIEnumPrompt = value['HMIEnumPrompt']
	command = value['command']
	if command in hMIEnumPrompt:
	
		tagPath = value['tagPath']
		jsonString = system.util.jsonEncode(hMIEnumPrompt[command])
		prompt = system.util.jsonDecode(jsonString)
		
		#Alsway Add TagPath to Parameters
		prompt["parameters"]["TagPath"]=tagPath
		prompt["parameters"]["Command"]=command
		return prompt
	
	return {"viewPath":""}
